<para>
  This thresholding method uses the triangle algorithm.  It is a
  wrapper around <ulink
  url="https://scikit-image.org/docs/stable/api/skimage.filters.html#skimage.filters.threshold_triangle"><code>skimage.filters.threshold_triangle</code></ulink>
  from &skimage;.
</para>
<para>
   The &image; is first converted from color to grayscale if
   necessary.
</para>

